    ", x * n (s)) is the unique mild solution of the closed loop system dx * i (s) = Ax * i (s) + bx * i (s) + cx * n (s) + ηx * i (s) + χx * n (s) + eγ * (D x i V n (s, x * (s))) 0) ds + σ dW (s),",
